name: Dreaded Imperial Starfleet
Lore: 'The Empire uses short-range fighters and patrol craft to maintain a presence in every system within its scope of power.',
Text: 'Deploy on your side of table. Once per turn, you may cancel a Force drain by placing her from hand any non-unique starfighter. Starfighters may deploy from here as if from hand (if Effect canceled by opponent, any starfighters here may immediately deploy for free).',
